::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe growls as he is pished back against some object, his body 
relaxing and leaning on it. He looks over at the femm, wondering if he should 
kill her. He was about to decide yes when he realized that the effort of 
transforming into robot mode alone would probably put him into stasis, much 
less killing this femm.

"Yes," he says quietly, "A drink would be fine... How did I get here?"

He had no choise but to use her to heal him, and then he would probably kill 
her, as he ussually did to anyone he had met.
